data.description:
Discover the allure of this waterfront 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in a well-established neighborhood. Boasting a 2-car attached garage, this residence showcases a thoughtfully designed open and split floorplan, NO CARPET and welcoming you with fresh paint, creating an inviting move-in-ready ambiance.

Generous storage options abound, with exceptionally spacious closets in every bedroom. The primary suite is a sanctuary with captivating water views, a vast walk-in closet featuring wooden shelving and heavy-duty rods, and an ensuite bathroom complete with a separate shower, soaking tub, dual sinks, and a secluded water closet nook.

The kitchen is a culinary haven, featuring a corner walk-in pantry with wood shelving, granite countertops, and a suite of appliances including a refrigerator, dishwasher, disposal, microwave, and gas range. The utility room, conveniently housing a washer and dryer, is easily accessible off the garage entry.

The exterior is adorned with low-maintenance brick and vinyl siding. The backyard, bordered by neighboring fences on both sides, offers the flexibility for the buyer to retain the scenic waterfront view with or without a back fence.

Additional features include a security system for peace of mind. Enjoy the convenience of a short and easy drive to both New Orleans (NOLA) and the Mississippi Gulf Coast. The Lakeshore Villages community enriches your lifestyle with various amenities such as playgrounds, fishing piers, party pavilions, a community pool, clubhouse, and more. Embrace a lifestyle of comfort and serenity in this exquisite waterfront home.
